Class Login

java.lang.Object
  util.Login
All Implemented Interfaces:
Config, CommonConfig, SimpleObserver
public class Login
extends java.lang.Object
implements SimpleObserver, Config

this runs the boardspace login process, by putting up a UI to collect the particulars, then invoking the standard login form on the server and parsing the result. The results are stored in a hashtable which is eventually used to server ersatz "applet" parameters.
